Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 看起来很美味啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏做的杯蛋糕果然最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个 我们为什么在这里集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于克雷仙多音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到克雷仙多音调有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能正确使用那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以打败所有负向音调了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能正确使用呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接问克雷仙多音调就好了 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克雷仙多音调 请出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们 想要正确使用克雷仙多音调的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:01:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们自己思考！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi Rere Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样做 Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请更加爱惜些 Mimi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要正确使用克雷仙多音调的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要提升光之美少女的力量 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特训！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二！光之美少女的宿营大作战喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 等了很久吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你好慢哦 响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 要准备很多东西耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莲 你这身装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从音吉先生那里借来的书学习到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起露营 那就是青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起青春 那就是吉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家一起唱歌吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青春歌曲前十名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露营是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提升光之美少女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顽强地克服艰苦的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使我们正确使用克雷仙多音调的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这么热血的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常的激动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这是我第一次露营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发去露营吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 提升光之美少女的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我们也要提升力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道快速提升力量的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀~呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜 呜呜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我们到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里的路上 完全就是特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸作曲时会隐居在这里的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说今天黄昏的时候也会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要露营 就住在那个房子里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样 就没有气氛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 露营才有青春的感觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有多喜欢青春呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 把行李放下 开始进行空手道的特训吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 空手道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是正拳突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没有精神！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次 喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是前踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 腰身这么不稳！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一击 每一击都要燃烧你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~呜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~哇啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吼~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这样的练法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想更加开心地特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能开心地特训呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来 换我来当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二！一二！一二！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二！一二！一二！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 用力出拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 很开心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开心是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛮开心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不燃烧起来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 有好好地锻炼到肌肉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说 武道在肉体锻炼的同时也包括了精神锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神锻炼就交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到精神锻炼 那就是坐禅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从音吉先生那借来的书上查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音吉先生的爱好到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得这样可以提升光之美少女的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啪 疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐禅 是端正你的姿态在坐着的状态下达到精神统一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍掉一切的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速力量提升方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是把这里的力量咖喱全部吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超大分量的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟内吃完就能免费
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚 麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚没有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底 要做到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能最先放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先提出坐禅的是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知从何时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐禅比赛变成了忍耐比赛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 谁赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起 哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人一起放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家和谐了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 咖喱之后是体力增强拉面！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 是巨大鱿鱼盖饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 是汉堡包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和猪排盖饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后 是巨大的甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量说不定就提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是变得好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是青春啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要早起 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爬山吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在山顶上看日出很美哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米也赞成爬山喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女之间的羁绊 也会变得更强喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流星 流星 流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米也睡吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是音符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于到最难的难关了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏 艾莲 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点就到山顶了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 让我来帮你们拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不自己拿就不算特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起一个人努力 三人的合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 坐禅的时候想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起一个人努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人的心合而为一！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 和声力量 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己的力量有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我身体很轻先上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找最容易爬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我应该做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏在最后面跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要带着你平时那种温柔的笑容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 对！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方 从左侧爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左边是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就快看到山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了喵 响？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 果然三个背包还是很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是“不在此做个了结的话 我就不是女人！”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦啊~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 响？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微有些大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就到山顶了不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 三个人一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三人的心连在一起了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 Dodo！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调在城里暴走了 Rere！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodo Rere Lala
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏吧！光之美少女 转调！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指尖弹奏的是狂野的曲调 旋律天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指尖弹奏的是柔和的曲调 节奏天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指尖弹奏的是灵魂的曲调 节拍天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传送吧 三人的组曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜~哇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negatone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下停下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真狼狈啊 光之美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒她们 负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nega
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的负向音调 很强！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们的力量 也应该提升了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nega
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你那一个滚筒将光之美少女碾碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过这次的露营 我们发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女的力量 并不是强大！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们遇上困难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的心合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相帮助战胜困难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚筒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和声力量在提升喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nega
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克雷仙多音调
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 光之美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 所有的旋律之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们传送
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望的交响曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女 组曲 时光乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵噗 喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sisi 席利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的旋律 马上就要完成了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是特训的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是克雷仙多音调 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个力量如此强大 莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯天使 怎么办 Dodo？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下 Dodo！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩的和声力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也多亏了克雷仙多音调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们注意到了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后 你们也要同心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起战胜困难！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走一走！瞧一瞧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由市场开业了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有招财猫迎接大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在购买的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还将超值奉送这个漂亮的宝石盒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把治愈音乐盒当作赠品喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒！？没有了？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治愈音乐盒消失了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦啰哦啰~！治愈音乐盒被偷了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让心中响起和声的力量吧！
